title: Rumor: iPhone 14 Pro could have the most RAM in any iPhone yet
content:
In about seven months, Apple will unveil the next generation of iPhones. With that, a new rumor suggests the company will add 8GB of RAM to the iPhone 14 Pro.

more…

description: A new rumor suggests that Apple will jump from 6GB of RAM on the iPhone 13 Pro to 8GB of RAM on the iPhone 14 Pro.
